		"description": "<blockquote><p>Finesse, Loading, Range (10/30)</p></blockquote><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>When this weapon is used to hit a target with a melee weapon attack, you can use your reaction to fire the gun in the handle, gaining a <strong>1d6</strong> expertise die on an immediate ranged weapon attack against the same target.</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>When exposed to freezing temperatures the blade of this magic sword sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet.</p><p>While you are attuned to the sword, attacks using it deal an extra 1d6 cold damage and you gain resistance to fire damage.</p><p>Once per hour, when you draw the sword you can choose to extinguish all nonmagical flames within 30 feet.</p>",
